we can follow the clues

44
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,730
to uncover the traitor in Susha.

45
00:02:34,730 --> 00:02:35,390
Oh, come on!

46
00:02:35,390 --> 00:02:36,470
Do we even need to investigate?

47
00:02:36,470 --> 00:02:37,000
It's most likely

48
