when we left Zhengnian Villa?

64
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:09,000
Treat guests with hospitality.

65
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,260
Take good care of them.

66
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,420
Your Highness.

67
