But for the lady's

80
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,930
damaged meridians,

81
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,470
it won't be of much help.

82
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,560
Besides, this belongs to
the Second Prince...

83
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,680
My brother gave it to me,

84
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,590
