156
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:46,480
Take good care of my wife.

157
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,560
Yes.

158
00:07:50,190 --> 00:07:51,000
My lady,

159
00:07:51,270 --> 00:07:52,390
