167
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,310
Get out!

168
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:04,590
Don't you understand what I'm saying?

169
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:05,630
My lady,

170
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,000
please change your clothes,

171
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,970
